metadata.name: Just For Fun @BAYC Pass
metadata.description: Just For Fun @BAYC - a total of 1000 BAYC Pass will be launched with holders granted the privileges of being the pioneering members of the BAYC IP DAO, first of its kind not only in Hong Kong but around the globe. Each and every member of Just For Fun @BAYC will be collectively holding the use right of the BAYC IP and will be bearing the duty to develop and enhance the influences of BAYC.
